| id | name    | address          | city        | ph_no      |
+----+---------+------------------+-------------+------------+
|  1 | Amrutha | Kizhaketheruvath | Eranjipalam | 9234567865 |
|  2 | Anna    | narikuni         | malapuram   | 3234567865 |
|  6 | Divya   | sreevalsam       | calicut     | 9567098504 |
